\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {7}{\ignorespaces Convergence by initialisation scheme. Standard $\mathcal  {N}(0,1)$ (red) triggers a gradient explosion at epoch~$\approx 75$ (MSE peaks at~3.3) but ultimately converges to the lowest test MAE. He normal/uniform converge stably and reach comparable performance.}}{14}{figure.caption.20}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:fnn_init}{{7}{14}{Convergence by initialisation scheme. Standard $\mathcal {N}(0,1)$ (red) triggers a gradient explosion at epoch~$\approx 75$ (MSE peaks at~3.3) but ultimately converges to the lowest test MAE. He normal/uniform converge stably and reach comparable performance}{figure.caption.20}{}}
