\newlabel{fig:fnn_optimizer}{{8}{15}{Convergence by optimizer. Plain SGD at three learning rates and SGD with momentum $\mu =0.9$ (with and without LR decay). Momentum dominates all plain-SGD variants; adding decay changes nothing under early stopping}{figure.caption.23}{}}
